title: 820-3115 no power
message:
No liquid damage. All power rails are present except for CPU VCIORE. U7400 was shorted. Replaced and short gone however still no CPU VCORE.

R7403 and R7402 are 180k and 150K both around 12.40V

What should be checked next?

title: 820-3115 no power
message:
CPU could be damaged too.
Compare diode mode on VCORE with known good board.

Try new BIOS file.
